{"word":"ἀργύριον","slug":"ἀργύριον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀργύριον</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a piece of silver, a silver coin</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>collectively, <i>money, a sum of money, cash</i>, as we also say <i>\"silver\"</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>= <a href='S:ἄργυρος'><el>ἄργυρος</el></a>, <i>silver</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}